Delete a directory
============================================
hdfs dfs -rm -r /user/ambili/testjob




put file to hdfs
--------------------------------------
hdfs dfs -put file.txt /user/shyam




Add a file to HDFS from local file system 
-------------------------------------------------
hdfs dfs -put file.txt /user/ambili/file.txt




Running wordcount job
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
hadoop jar wordcount.jar com.hadoop.wordcount.WordCount /user/ambili/file.txt /user/shyam/wordcountoutput


View file
-----------------------------------------------
hadoop fs -cat /user/ambili/file.txt